            <h1 class="normal__title">LAWS</h1>
            <p class="normal__para">The Constitution of India, 1950 is the foremost law that deals with the framework of
                the codes, procedures, fundamental rights and duties of citizens and powers, and duties of government.
                The laws in India are interconnected with each other forming a hybrid legal system.</p>
            <div class="recently__container container grid">
